def-group:
Disable the AlwaysAdmit Admission Control Plugin
multi_platform_ocp
To ensure OpenShift only responses to requests explicitly allowed by the admissions control plugin, remove any instance of AlwaysAdmit for the admission control plugin.
{{%- if product == "ocp4" %}}
/etc/kubernetes/static-pod-resources/configmaps/config/config.yaml ^.*"serviceAccountPublicKeyFiles":[\s]*\[.*"(\S+)".*\][,]*.*$ 1
{{% else %}}
/etc/origin/master/master-config.yaml ^[\s]*admissionConfig\:(?:[^\n]*\n+)+?[\s]*pluginConfig\:(?:[^\n]*\n+)+?[\s]*AlwaysAdmit\:[\s]*$ 1
{{%- endif %}}
